So what if l don't have work?
l still have money.

575
01:16:27,247 --> 01:16:30,444
l have a good feeling though.

576
01:16:32,152 --> 01:16:34,951
My horoscope says l'll be
lucky tomorrow

577
01:16:35,055 --> 01:16:38,252
l wouldn't lose a bet!

578
01:16:39,993 --> 01:16:44,157
l'll win the daily double!
l fucking will!

579
01:16:45,466 --> 01:16:48,766
Suck my big one!

580
01:17:46,059 --> 01:17:47,891
No losing, my ass!

581
01:17:51,732 --> 01:17:55,498
The horses hate me too!

582
01:17:55,969 --> 01:18:00,907
Times are bad but a
little win wouldn't hurt...

583
01:18:01,141 --> 01:18:03,007
They win, l lose.

584
01:18:05,078 --> 01:18:07,479
Right, Kokone?

585
01:18:08,682 --> 01:18:11,242
That's not true. Cheer up.

586
01:18:23,096 --> 01:18:27,363
Am l hallucinating from the drink?
Or is it paranormal?

587
01:18:30,771 --> 01:18:33,536
Do you hear me?

588
01:18:34,942 --> 01:18:37,206
l'm no good.

589
01:18:38,345 --> 01:18:42,077
