l don't deserve to live.

590
01:18:42,182 --> 01:18:46,016
lt'd be better for eveyone
if l died!

591
01:18:46,386 --> 01:18:48,946
By gas, knife or hanging...

592
01:18:49,423 --> 01:18:51,448
You can pull my legs then.

593
01:18:54,862 --> 01:18:56,660
Gas is too catastrophic.

594
01:19:03,003 --> 01:19:04,198
You know what?

595
01:19:05,005 --> 01:19:06,166
l can do it

596
