sitting down like this.

597
01:19:13,080 --> 01:19:15,276
l can hang myself sitting.

598
01:19:21,989 --> 01:19:25,391
You're not useless. Cheer up.

599
01:20:06,800 --> 01:20:08,632
What's to be cheery about?

600
01:20:13,073 --> 01:20:14,871
l won't fall for that.

601
01:20:26,053 --> 01:20:27,145
Who are you?

602
01:20:29,022 --> 01:20:31,047
l'm with you every day.

603
01:20:32,092 --> 01:20:33,389
l'll help you change.

604
01:20:35,362 --> 01:20:36,557
You're...

605
01:20:37,864 --> 01:20:39,832
the lifesize figure.

606
01:20:43,737 --> 01:20:45,831
Who are you really?

607
01:20:47,140 --> 01:20:50,508
Did you turn into a human
at the building?

608
01:20:51,511 --> 01:20:53,741
l thought l imagined it...

609
01:20:56,416 --> 01:20:58,180
l am Kokone.

610
01:21:03,590 --> 01:21:04,989
Listen...

611
01:21:07,894 --> 01:21:09,384
Listen to me!

612
01:21:13,767 --> 01:21:14,928
Ouch!

613
01:21:16,703 --> 01:21:17,761
Wait.

614
01:21:27,614 --> 01:21:28,604
So you're...

615
01:21:30,450 --> 01:21:31,849
a human?

616
01:21:37,758 --> 01:21:40,887
What are you?
Stop fooling around!

617
01:21:41,628 --> 01:21:44,620
l'm drunk but l'm not!

618
01:21:57,277 --> 01:21:58,904
Don't be rough.

619
01:22:07,554 --> 01:22:10,421
l won't let them tread on me!

620
01:22:11,324 --> 01:22:14,783
l won't stay down without
a fight!

621
01:22:17,297 --> 01:22:18,230
lt hurts.

622
01:22:19,433 --> 01:22:20,832
Be gentle.

623
01:22:29,509 --> 01:22:30,943
Kentaro!

624
01:24:15,182 --> 01:24:17,947
Tilt a little.

625
01:24:18,919 --> 01:24:19,784
How's that?

626
01:26:22,208 --> 01:26:26,839
l'm running out of money.

627
01:26:28,248 --> 01:26:31,081
But there are always loan sharks.

628
01:26:31,751 --> 01:26:32,912
OK.

629
01:26:36,756 --> 01:26:38,622
l'm good at mahjong.

630
01:26:39,926 --> 01:26:43,590
l'll win big and make money

631
01:26:44,831 --> 01:26:47,425
so l can start looking for work.

632
01:26:48,735 --> 01:26:50,225
But l've been unlucky.

633
01:26:52,172 --> 01:26:55,699
So l want you to help me
win a game.

634
01:26:58,578 --> 01:27:01,013
Tell me what moves to make.

635
01:27:02,949 --> 01:27:07,511
Don't worry. You are lucky.

636
01:27:08,822 --> 01:27:11,314
Just believe in yourself.

637
01:27:12,792 --> 01:27:14,089
Besides

638
01:27:15,228 --> 01:27:18,630
l know nothing about mahjong.

639
01:27:20,133 --> 01:27:21,532
Just pick one.

640
01:27:23,470 --> 01:27:25,131
Da Shan Yuan...

641
01:27:25,739 --> 01:27:27,901
13 Orphans, 9 Gates of Heaven.

642
01:27:29,943 --> 01:27:33,709
9 Gates of Heaven sounds good.

643
01:27:35,315 --> 01:27:36,805
9 Gates!

644
01:27:39,552 --> 01:27:43,147
The chance of winning with 9 Gates
is one in a million.

645
01:27:44,391 --> 01:27:46,485
l'll go for it!

646
01:27:52,999 --> 01:27:54,398
l'll do it.

647
01:27:56,403 --> 01:27:58,132
You're my lucky star.

648
01:27:58,972 --> 01:28:02,340
l'll win with
9 Gates of Heaven!

649
01:28:04,811 --> 01:28:06,074
You can do it.

650
01:28:08,148 --> 01:28:12,608
See you later.
l'll go for 9 Gates of Heaven.

651
01:28:13,520 --> 01:28:15,511
Good luck?

652
01:28:32,372 --> 01:28:34,966
9 Gates of Heaven!

653
01:28:35,475 --> 01:28:38,376
9 Gates of Heaven!

654
01:28:38,545 --> 01:28:39,478
Call.

655
01:28:54,227 --> 01:28:55,217
My hand stinks...

656
01:28:55,361 --> 01:28:56,624
l'm going mahjong!

657
01:28:58,231 --> 01:29:02,168
Three Color Runs! Quad meld!

658
01:29:02,969 --> 01:29:04,403
Not again...

659
01:29:06,239 --> 01:29:09,231
I've been chanting 9 Gates of Heaven.

660
01:29:09,342 --> 01:29:11,743
And nothing happens.

661
01:29:29,896 --> 01:29:30,920
Call.

662
01:29:37,036 --> 01:29:38,401
Mahjong!

663
01:29:39,472 --> 01:29:41,031
l have 2 pairs.

664
01:29:43,243 --> 01:29:45,940
The dealer Wns. 12,OOO points.

665
01:29:46,212 --> 01:29:48,078
That's not fair...

666
01:29:58,725 --> 01:29:59,988
Kokone, please...

667
01:30:03,029 --> 01:30:05,020
Kokone, l love you.

668
01:30:06,966 --> 01:30:09,799
Kokone, l love you...

669
01:30:33,826 --> 01:30:37,922
Kokone, l love you...

670
01:30:55,148 --> 01:30:56,946
lt's looking good?

671
01:30:58,084 --> 01:30:59,176
l can win.

672
01:31:18,905 --> 01:31:23,138
I thought 9 Gates was impossibte
but l'm close?

673
01:31:26,145 --> 01:31:29,308
There's no going back.
l trust her.

674
01:31:29,649 --> 01:31:31,310
Kokone.

675
01:31:39,025 --> 01:31:42,461
Come on eighty-thousand?

676
01:31:52,205 --> 01:31:53,400
Call!

677
01:31:54,841 --> 01:31:57,242
Oh, couldn't you wait?

678
01:32:01,914 --> 01:32:04,576
l love you, Kokone.

679
01:32:10,990 --> 01:32:12,924
Kokone, l love you.

680
01:32:13,993 --> 01:32:15,188
Come on!

681
01:32:19,399 --> 01:32:20,560
Yes!

682
01:32:21,401 --> 01:32:24,098
l won with 9 Gates of Heaven!

683
01:32:25,805 --> 01:32:29,639
Did you hear that, guys?
9 Gates of Heaven!

684
01:32:30,410 --> 01:32:32,606
l'm the luckiest bastard!

685
01:32:32,712 --> 01:32:36,478
l did it! Thank you, Kokone!

686
01:32:37,684 --> 01:32:39,277
Pay up, pay up!

687
01:32:40,053 --> 01:32:42,579
Winning 9 Gates might kill you.

688
01:32:44,624 --> 01:32:46,592
Watch out for cars.

689
01:32:47,894 --> 01:32:53,230
lt's so rare to win 9 Gates,
you've used up all your luck.

690
01:32:53,466 --> 01:32:55,628
Go home! l'm done.

691
01:32:57,437 --> 01:33:00,668
l have to go back to
the love of my life!

692
01:33:04,344 --> 01:33:06,642
She's my lucky star?

693
01:33:06,779 --> 01:33:11,580
And my lucky star loves me?
l couldn't be happier?

694
01:33:12,151 --> 01:33:13,243
Awesome?

695
01:33:16,989 --> 01:33:20,550
The lights are kind of far.
l'll cross here.

696
01:33:21,194 --> 01:33:25,495
The cars will dodge me
because l'm so lucky.

697
01:33:34,006 --> 01:33:35,496
Watch out!

698
01:33:41,647 --> 01:33:42,512
l'm back!

699
01:33:44,484 --> 01:33:47,647
Kokone! l did like you said
and won!

700
01:33:52,158 --> 01:33:53,319
Kokone.

701
01:34:01,968 --> 01:34:03,299
Kokone?

702
01:34:11,744 --> 01:34:12,973
Okay...

703
01:34:15,882 --> 01:34:17,350
She's gone.

704
01:34:20,219 --> 01:34:22,119
She's left me.

705
01:34:38,104 --> 01:34:39,469
l see.

706
01:34:48,080 --> 01:34:49,514
lt makes sense.

707
01:34:54,187 --> 01:34:56,485
Nobody stays.

708
01:34:59,058 --> 01:35:01,686
Being with me isn't fun.

709
01:35:10,403 --> 01:35:16,137
lf she'd waited a little more
it would've been heaven.

710
01:35:28,955 --> 01:35:31,253
Oh, shut up...

711
01:35:35,795 --> 01:35:39,925
You idiot! Don't sing
in the middle of the night!

712
01:36:10,630 --> 01:36:16,694
Just wait where you are.
My dear girl

713
01:36:18,137 --> 01:36:23,303
Because l'm coming home soon

714
01:36:24,544 --> 01:36:30,244
You don't need to
show your tears

715
01:36:31,317 --> 01:36:36,221
l will never go far

716
01:36:37,990 --> 01:36:43,622
One day. someday

717
01:36:44,030 --> 01:36:48,627
A bad day like today

718
01:36:50,002 --> 01:36:56,169
We will shrug it off
with a smile

719
01:36:56,676 --> 01:37:01,204
With just a little bit of luck

720
01:37:02,682 --> 01:37:08,678
Even if you can't see me

721
01:37:09,755 --> 01:37:15,091
l'll always be nearby

722
01:37:16,262 --> 01:37:21,894
Just reach out your hand to me

723
01:37:22,902 --> 01:37:27,840
You'll feel your hand in mine

724
01:37:29,375 --> 01:37:35,178
As long as you think of me

725
01:37:35,548 --> 01:37:40,418
forever and ever more

726
01:37:42,088 --> 01:37:47,891
l will stay right by your heart

727
01:37:48,995 --> 01:37:54,456
And never go away

728
01:39:34,366 --> 01:39:37,392
Don't worry. Cheer up.

729
01:39:38,771 --> 01:39:40,535
