- Listen.

730
01:39:40,973 --> 01:39:44,876
l won because l did
what you said.

731
01:39:45,177 --> 01:39:47,612
l'm not loaded yet
but l'm getting lucky.

732
01:39:47,680 --> 01:39:48,772
l'm not a loser!

733
01:39:49,181 --> 01:39:50,706
l'm happy for you.

734
01:39:52,218 --> 01:39:54,380
l'm happy to have helped you.

735
01:39:55,888 --> 01:39:57,014
Dance with me.

