737
01:40:01,994 --> 01:40:04,361
Yes, you can.

738
01:40:11,070 --> 01:40:14,529
lt's no big deal,
it's just mahjong.

739
01:40:17,910 --> 01:40:19,241
Thank you.

740
01:40:27,019 --> 01:40:29,852
lt was almost ruined.

741
01:40:32,391 --> 01:40:34,018
How?

742
01:40:34,093 --> 01:40:37,893
Just when things started to look up

743
01:40:38,030 --> 01:40:41,989
a speeding truck came
zooming toward me!

744
01:40:42,067 --> 01:40:45,901
l ran and leaped and
there was a scream!

745
01:40:46,305 --> 01:40:48,069
What happened?

746
01:40:48,741 --> 01:40:54,544
They say there are 2 people in the
world who look like you.

747
01:40:55,948 --> 01:40:58,417
She looked exactly
like you, Kokone.

748
01:40:59,852 --> 01:41:02,412
She left without thanking me.

749
01:41:02,888 --> 01:41:06,256
What were you doing
with a woman?

750
01:41:06,625 --> 01:41:08,753
How could you?

751
01:41:08,861 --> 01:41:10,590
No, l wasn't!

752
01:41:11,897 --> 01:41:13,092
Let's dance.

753
01:42:12,658 --> 01:42:14,148
Congratulations!

754
01:42:21,133 --> 01:42:26,128
